desert nomad mercenary eastern~
a desert nomad mercenary~
A desert nomad mercenary surveys the eastern trade route with calculating eyes.
~
One of the many mercenary groups that operate in the eastern desert margins, the nomad mercenary is hired by various caravans for security and by others for precisely the opposite purpose. They do not advertise which contract they are currently fulfilling.
~
